Task: Add a Collaborative Red Teaming (CRT) view to the existing Osprey Policy UI
Goal. Surface the new src/crt MVP in the existing Osprey Policy UI as an additive view — campaigns, the attribution-blind coverage map, diversity, participating-org count, contribution credits, and the CRTReport (with hash). Match the Policy UI's current stack and components; do not reinvent styling or add a parallel app.

Depends on: A.5-MVP (the src/crt/ package) being present, or at least its models.py + CoverageMap/CRTReport. If the CRT read-API isn't wired yet, the view must still render from a static fixture (see §4) so the UI can be demoed independently.


