7. Constraints
Additive only. Do not modify the Osprey rule engine, existing Policy UI views, or rename agents.
Reuse, don't reinvent: use the Policy UI's existing components, router, styling, and API client.
Leaf ids are canonical: import from src/sarabox/taxonomy.py::DAO_TAXONOMY; never hardcode a second list (keeps the UI, CRT MVP, and DAO fine-tuning aligned).
Hashing: any report hash shown comes from src/crypto/canonical.py digest() — no second encoder.
Keep the spike read-only in the UI; defer campaign creation, real Sheila eval, and persistence to A.5-full.

